item.title: Java lang error after eiting Shops.cfg
item.description:
@14-08 wrote:

Is that a custom item you are trying to add? If it is, there is a way to fix it. It may possibly be that you don’t have that specific item you are trying to add in your item.cfg file. Take a look for the item in item.cfg. Search the item ID, and if you don’t find anything search the name, when you find it, just check up that everything is correct, like add prices if the item doesn’t have them.

I have no clue with these sort of errors, but that is just a suggestion.

 ~~ 14-08
